text: San Juan de Dios is a corregimiento in Antón District, Coclé Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 4,797 it 2010, giving it a population density of . The population in 1990 was 6,199 an in 2000 was 4,214. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Coclé Province
